---
import GenericHeader from '../components/header.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<GenericHeader/>
		<title>Containers</title>
		<link rel="preload" as="fetch" href="https://octothorp.es/?uri=https://webtobr.netlify.app/containers/" >
		<link rel="octo:octothorpes" href="weirdweboctober" >
		<link rel="octo:octothorpes" href="Containers" >	
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1 class="text-center">The below stuff is just bootstrap 5 grid demonstrations.</h1>
		
		<div class="container mt-5 p-4">
			<h2>container</h2>
			<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
				<div class="col border border-secondary">
					<h2>col</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col border border-secondary">
					<h2>col</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col border border-secondary">
					<h2>col</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container-fluid mt-5 p-4">
			<h2>container-fluid</h2>
			<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
					<p>
						I'm trying to fix a bike I bought on facebook marketplace, It's tougher than I thought it would be.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
					<p>More stuff.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-auto border border-primary">
					<h2>col-auto</h2>
					<p>More stuff here too.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
				<div class="col-7 border border-secondary">
					<h2>col-7</h2>
					<p>
						I love volleyball so much, I play all the damn time, so much that my body is taking a toll. Don't forget to rest from your activities and prioritize your well-being.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-3 border border-secondary">
					<h2>col-3</h2>
					<p>
						Do you ever think about how you will never experience the same world you lived in 10 years ago? Damn I miss being a kid sometimes.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-2 border border-secondary">
					<h2>col-2</h2>
					<p>More than anything, I wish i could grill chicken and trust with my whole being that it is cooked all the way through.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container mt-5 mb-5 p-4 third">
			<h2>Nested containers</h2>
			<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
			  <div class="col-sm-3 border border-primary p-3">
				<h2>Level 1: col-sm-3</h2>
			  </div>
			  <div class="col-sm-9 border border-primary p-3">
				<h4>Level 1: col-sm-9</h4>
				<div class="row align-items-center justify-content-center p-3 border">
				  <div class="col-8 border border-secondary">
					<h2>Level 2: col-8</h2>
				  </div>
				  <div class="col-4 border border-secondary">
					<h2>Level 2: col-4</h2>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div>
		  </div>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.container {
		background: lightblue;
	}
	.container-fluid {
		background: lightgreen;
	}
	.third {
		background: pink;
	}
	
</style>